|===
|Path|Type|Description

|`+entries+`
|`+Array+`
|An Array of Entry object

|`+entries[].uri+`
|`+String+`
|Entry URI

|`+entries[].provider+`
|`+String+`
|Entry provider

|`+entries[].title+`
|`+String+`
|Entry title

|`+entries[].thumbnail+`
|`+String+`
|Entry thumbnail url

|`+entries[].liked+`
|`+Boolean+`
|Entry like state

|`+entries[].meta+`
|`+String+`
|Entry meta information used in core server

|===
